name: Noise-Neon 001
description:
Noise-Neons are OBJKTs that are only revealed after the first trade. Once the true shape has been revealed, it will stick to that shape forever. The shape is determined by the wallet-address of the first collector.

Every Noise-Neon is a unique OBJKT (Edition of 1) and therefore a true NFT.

Noise-Neons is a project by @TeNinEightNFTs
For more information about Noise-Neons visit noiseneons.tenineight.xyz

This OBJKT uses the hicdex API and therefore depends on it. This is all experimental and might break in the future. OBJKT uses p5js with p5.collide and p5.createloop.
